com.doubleclue.sdk.api

Interface AppSdkListener


  • public interface AppSdkListener
    This class the callback interface for the App SDK Library Methods are called asynchronously. Methods should return back as soon as possible. Long processing should be done on background tasks.

    • Method Detail

      • onReceiveMessage

        void onReceiveMessage(ReceivedMessage receivedMessage)
        This method is called when library receives a Server Message. Messages may require a definit responce within a certain timeout. Server sends onyl one Message at a time. Server may have a queue of messages
        Parameters:
        receivedMessage - see ReceivedMessage

      • onReceiveMessageTimedOut

        void onReceiveMessageTimedOut()
        This method is called, when a message with response required is received and the App did respond with the the message timeout. App should discard the message

      • onDisconnect

        void onDisconnect(String reason)
        A disconnect is received from server
        Parameters:
        reason - If null the disconnect is an App initiated disconnect.
